  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: Scientific notation for amount is shown on Sent Transaction screen  if it's opened from Unsigned tab or from chat via send command:\r\n![screenshot_20171009-184433](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/6584810/31346673-22ff12d4-ad1a-11e7-8135-8cd941056b02.png)\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nAmount is shown in usual format, e.g. `0.00000007`\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n Scientific notation for amount is shown `7e-8`\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Open 1-1 chat\r\n- send to Jarrad 0.1 eth\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: develop  0.9.10-179-g3225d1a2\r\n* Operating System: \r\nReal device iPhone 6s, iOs 10.3.1\r\nReal device iPhone 7 plus, iOs 11.0.2\r\nReal device Google Pixel XL, Android 8.0",
